(345, 1, 'admin/tour-trong-nuoc', 'POST', '127.0.0.1', '{\"code\":\"dn2\",\"title\":\"Du l\\u1ecbch \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng \\u2013 B\\u00e0 N\\u00e0 \\u2013 C\\u00f9 Lao Ch\\u00e0m Tour ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n T\\u1eeb TP. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh gi\\u00e1 khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u00e3i\",\"slug_tour\":null,\"amount\":\"25\",\"date_start\":\"H\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y\",\"start\":\"1\",\"city_id\":\"2\",\"description\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">NG\\u00c0Y 1: TP.h\\u1ed2 cH\\u00cd MINH \\u2013 \\u0110\\u00c0 N\\u1eb4NG \\u2013 B\\u00c1N \\u0110\\u1ea2O S\\u01a0N TR\\u00c0<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i s\\u00e1ng:&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 m\\u1eb7t t\\u1ea1i ga qu\\u1ed1c n\\u1ed9i, s\\u00e2n bay tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1edd bay \\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t hai ti\\u1ebfng.<\\/span><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n c\\u00f4ng ty Vietnam Travel \\u0111\\u00f3n v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 Qu\\u00fd Kh\\u00e1ch l\\u00e0m th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00f3n chuy\\u1ebfn bay \\u0111i&nbsp;\\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng. \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0110\\u00e0 n\\u1eb5ng, xe \\u0111\\u01b0a qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch v\\u1ec1 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i &nbsp;tr\\u01b0a:&nbsp; D\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa tr\\u01b0a t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng v\\u1edbi&nbsp;\\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng&nbsp;nh\\u01b0:&nbsp;\\u201cB\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng th\\u1ecbt heo 2 \\u0111\\u1ea7u da &amp; M\\u1ef3 Qu\\u1ea3ng\\u201d.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ec1u:&nbsp; \\u0110o\\u00e0n kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh tham quan:&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">B\\u00e1n \\u0110\\u1ea3o S\\u01a1n Tr\\u00e0&nbsp;(Monkey Mountain) quay m\\u1ed9t v\\u00f2ng quanh B\\u00e1n \\u0110\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ec3 m\\u1ee5c k\\u00edch to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea3nh ph\\u1ed1 bi\\u1ec3n \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng tr\\u00ean cao.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Vi\\u1ebfng&nbsp;Linh \\u1ee8ng T\\u1ef1&nbsp;\\u2013 n\\u01a1i c\\u00f3&nbsp;t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Ph\\u1eadt B\\u00e0 65m cao nh\\u1ea5t Vi\\u1ec7t Nam.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">T\\u1eafm bi\\u1ec3n M\\u1ef9 Kh\\u00ea&nbsp;\\u2013 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng \\u2013&nbsp;1 trong 6 b\\u00e3i bi\\u1ec3n quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169 nh\\u1ea5t h\\u00e0nh tinh (do t\\u1ea1p ch\\u00ed Fober \\u2013 M\\u1ef9 b\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ecdn)&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">D\\u00f9ng c\\u01a1m chi\\u1ec1u t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i &nbsp;t\\u1ed1i: Tham quan C\\u00f4ng vi\\u00ean Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c1 \\u2013 Asia Park \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng, b\\u00ean b\\u1edd T\\u00e2y s\\u00f4ng H\\u00e0n, s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1eefng n\\u00e9t \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o, m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c m\\u00f4 h\\u00ecnh gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ed tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng n\\u00e9t v\\u0103n h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1eadm ch\\u1ea5t \\u00c1 \\u0110\\u00f4ng (chi ph\\u00ed t\\u1ef1 t\\u00fac).&nbsp;&nbsp;Ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n 3*.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/Du%20lich%20da%20nang%20-%20hoi%20an-%20hue\\/Linh-ung-tu_viet-nam-travel.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:556px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:1000px\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">NG\\u00c0Y 2: C\\u00d9 LAO CH\\u00c0M \\u2013 PH\\u1ed0 C\\u1ed4 H\\u1ed8I AN<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i s\\u00e1ng:&nbsp;Sau b\\u1eefa s\\u00e1ng \\u1edf kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh tham quan:&nbsp;C\\u00f9 Lao Ch\\u00e0m ( ch\\u01b0a bao v\\u00e9 C\\u00f9 Lao)\\u2013 Khu D\\u1ef1 tr\\u1eef Sinh quy\\u1ec3n Th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi, m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ecba danh du l\\u1ecbch bi\\u1ec3n n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng c\\u1ee7a mi\\u1ec1n Trung. \\u0110\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u00e2y Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 dip kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 m\\u1ed9t v\\u00f9ng thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean hoang s\\u01a1, th\\u01a1 m\\u1ed9ng h\\u00f2a m\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0o cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng d\\u00e2n d\\u00e3 trong s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u00f3n ti\\u1ebfp n\\u1ed3ng h\\u1eadu c\\u1ee7a c\\u01b0 d\\u00e2n l\\u00e0ng chai; \\u2026\\u0110\\u1ebfn b\\u1ebfn t\\u00e0u c\\u1ea3ng&nbsp;C\\u1eeda \\u0110\\u1ea1i&nbsp;\\u0111o\\u00e0n l\\u00ean thuy\\u1ec1n cao t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ec3 vi\\u1ebfng th\\u0103m \\u0111\\u1ea3o C\\u00f9 Lao Ch\\u00e0m Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 d\\u1ecbp tham quan:<\\/span><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Ch\\u00f9a c\\u1ed5 H\\u1ea3i T\\u1ea1ng&nbsp;h\\u01a1n 400 tr\\u0103m n\\u0103m tu\\u1ed5i, th\\u0103m \\u201c \\u00c2u thuy\\u1ec1n\\u201d n\\u01a1i l\\u00e1nh b\\u00e3o c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c thuy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u00e1nh c\\u00e1 khi g\\u1eb7p th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft x\\u1ea5u v\\u00e0 t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u \\u0111\\u1eddi s\\u1ed1ng c\\u1ee7a c\\u01b0 d\\u00e2n chai l\\u01b0\\u1edbi s\\u1ed1ng tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ea3o t\\u1ea1i b\\u00e3i L\\u00e0ng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Khu du l\\u1ecbch B\\u00e3i B\\u1ea5c, Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch thay \\u0111\\u1ed3 t\\u1eafm bi\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0 l\\u1eb7n ng\\u1eafm san h\\u00f4 (Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch l\\u1eb7n n\\u1ed5i ng\\u1eafm san h\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1eb7t n\\u1ea1 v\\u00e0 \\u00f4ng th\\u1edf nh\\u1ef1a).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i &nbsp;tr\\u01b0a:&nbsp;\\u0102n tr\\u01b0a nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng&nbsp;C\\u00f9 Lao Ch\\u00e0m&nbsp;.&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 d\\u1ecbp th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1eadm \\u0111\\u00e0 h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb bi\\u1ec3n C\\u00f9 Lao Ch\\u00e0m nh\\u01b0: \\u1ed1c v\\u00fa n\\u00e0ng, cua \\u0111\\u00e1, t\\u00f4m, m\\u1ef1c \\u1ed1ng\\u2026<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ec1u:&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 do t\\u1eafm&nbsp;Bi\\u1ec3n C\\u00f9 Lao Ch\\u00e0m, \\u0111\\u1eafm m\\u00ecnh trong l\\u00e0n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc xanh m\\u00e1t v\\u1edbi b\\u00e3i c\\u00e1t tr\\u1eafng v\\u00e0 kh\\u00ed h\\u1eadu trong l\\u00e0nh.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c th\\u0103m khu b\\u1ea3o t\\u1ed3n bi\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0 tham gia c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng&nbsp;l\\u1eb7n bi\\u1ec3n (Snokelling)&nbsp;kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 san h\\u00f4\\u2026<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">V\\u1ec1 l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec1n kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh qua&nbsp;Ph\\u1ed1 C\\u1ed5&nbsp;H\\u1ed9i An&nbsp;b\\u00e1ch b\\u1ed9 tham quan v\\u00e0 mua s\\u1eafm Ph\\u1ed1 C\\u1ed5 v\\u1edbi: Ch\\u00f9a C\\u1ea7u Nh\\u1eadt B\\u1ea3n, Nh\\u00e0 C\\u1ed5 h\\u00e0ng tr\\u0103m n\\u0103m tu\\u1ed5i, H\\u1ed9i Qu\\u00e1n Ph\\u01b0\\u1edbc Ki\\u1ebfn &amp; X\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng m\\u1ef9 ngh\\u1ec7.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Tr\\u1edf v\\u1ec1 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng tham quan&nbsp;Ng\\u0169 H\\u00e0nh S\\u01a1n&nbsp;\\u2013 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c v\\u00ed nh\\u01b0 h\\u00f2n non b\\u1ed9 kh\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ed3 gi\\u1eefa l\\u00f2ng th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng v\\u1edbi \\u0110\\u1ed9ng Huy\\u1ec1n Kh\\u00f4ng, Ch\\u00f9a Linh \\u1ee8ng, Ch\\u00f9a Tam Thai, V\\u1ecdng H\\u1ea3i \\u0110\\u00e0i, \\u2026 mua s\\u1eafm qu\\u00e0 l\\u01b0u ni\\u1ec7m t\\u1ea1i l\\u00e0ng ngh\\u1ec1 \\u0111i\\u00eau kh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u00e1 Non N\\u01b0\\u1edbc.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">D\\u00f9ng c\\u01a1m chi\\u1ec1u t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i &nbsp;t\\u1ed1i: Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 do th\\u01b0\\u1edfng ngo\\u1ea1n&nbsp;du thuy\\u1ec1n tr\\u00ean s\\u00f4ng H\\u00e0n&nbsp;ng\\u1eafm c\\u1ea3nh&nbsp;\\u0110\\u00e0 Th\\u00e0nh&nbsp;v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u00eam, ho\\u1eb7c t\\u1ea3n b\\u1ed9 th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed trong l\\u00e0nh b\\u00ean&nbsp; b\\u1edd&nbsp;&nbsp;H\\u00e0n Giang v\\u1edbi t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng C\\u00e1 Ch\\u00e9p H\\u00f3a Long&nbsp;\\u2013 Bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng mong mu\\u1ed1n v\\u01b0\\u01a1n l\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng. &nbsp;Ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n 3*.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/Du%20lich%20da%20nang%20-%20hoi%20an-%20hue\\/Cham-Island-Tour.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:500px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:1000px\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">NG\\u00c0Y 3: B\\u00c0 N\\u00c0 N\\u00daI CH\\u00daA \\u2013 T\\u1eaeM BI\\u1ec2N M\\u1ef8 KH\\u00ca- TP. H\\u1ed2 CH\\u00cd MINH<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i s\\u00e1ng:&nbsp;D\\u00f9ng buffet s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi cao nguy\\u00ean&nbsp;B\\u00e0 N\\u00e0 ( ch\\u01b0a bao v\\u00e9 c\\u00e1p treo)&nbsp;n\\u01a1i c\\u00f3 kh\\u00ed h\\u1eadu Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng v\\u1edbi tuy\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1p treo k\\u1ef7 l\\u1ee5c m\\u1edbi c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u2013 Ng\\u1eafm to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea3nh th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng t\\u1eeb tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1p treo&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">L\\u00ean Cao Nguy\\u00ean Bana Hills Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 do tham quan, khu vui ch\\u01a1i gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ed t\\u1ea1i B\\u00e0 N\\u00e0:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">C\\u00f4ng Vi\\u00ean Fantasy&nbsp;v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c tr\\u00f2 ch\\u01a1i phi\\u00eau l\\u01b0u m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1 nh\\u01b0: V\\u00f2ng Quay T\\u00ecnh Y\\u00eau, Phi C\\u00f4ng Skiver, \\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0110ua L\\u1eeda, Ng\\u00f4i Nh\\u00e0 Ma.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">R\\u1ea1p chi\\u1ebfu phim 3D Mega 360 \\u0111\\u1ed9&nbsp;v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i nh\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 duy nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 \\u1edf Vi\\u00eat Nam, Hai r\\u1ea1p chi\\u1ebfu phim 4D v\\u00e0 5Di, Xe Tr\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u1ed0ng, H\\u1ea7m r\\u01b0\\u1ee3u, V\\u01b0\\u1eddn hoa t\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau,<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">B\\u1ea3o T\\u00e0ng S\\u00e1p&nbsp;tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y h\\u01a1n 40 t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u00e1p nh\\u1eefng nh\\u00e2n v\\u1eadt n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi\\u2026<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111i ch\\u00f9a c\\u1ea7u b\\u00ecnh an v\\u00e0 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe cho gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh:&nbsp;Ch\\u00f9a Linh \\u1ee8ng, \\u0110\\u1ec1n L\\u0129nh Ch\\u00faa Linh T\\u1eeb, Th\\u00e1p Linh Phong T\\u1ef1, T\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Th\\u00edch Ca M\\u00e2u Ni, L\\u1ea7u Chu\\u00f4ng, Nh\\u00e0 Bia, Mi\\u1ebfu B\\u00e0, Tr\\u00fa V\\u0169 Tr\\u00e0 Qu\\u00e1n.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\