h ta\\u0323i \\u0111i\\u00ea\\u0309m he\\u0323n kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u00e0 ga T2 s\\u00e2n bay Qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf N\\u1ed9i B\\u00e0i, Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch l\\u00e0m th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00e1p chuy\\u1ebfn bay VJ901 (12h15 \\u2013 15h50) \\u0111i&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(10, 89, 212); text-decoration-line: none;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>du l\\u1ecbch Th\\u00e1i Lan<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/a>.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 t\\u00fac \\u0103n tr\\u01b0a (chi ph\\u00ed t\\u1ef1 t\\u00fac)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">\\u0110\\u1ebfn s\\u00e2n bay qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf Suvanabhumi Th\\u00e1i Lan, \\u0111o\\u00e0n l\\u00e0m th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c nh\\u1eadp c\\u1ea3nh.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>T\\u1ed1i:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span>Xe \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111o\\u00e0n \\u0111i \\u0103n t\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng. Ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh v\\u1ec1&nbsp; Bangkok tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111i Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch ng\\u1eafm c\\u1ea3nh th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 Bangkok lung linh v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u00eam v\\u00e0 t\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Bayjoke Sky cao nh\\u1ea5t Th\\u00e1i Lan ( 86 t\\u1ea7ng )<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n S.D AVENUE BANGKOK ho\\u1eb7c t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 02: BANGKOK -&nbsp;<\\/strong><strong>WAT TRAIMIT \\u2013 WAT SAKET \\u2013 TIGER ZOO \\u2013 PATTAYA (\\u0102N S\\u00c1NG \\/ TR\\u01afA\\/T\\u1ed0I)<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>S\\u00e1ng:<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch \\u0103n s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n. Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 xe \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111oa\\u0300n tham quan, chi\\u00eam b\\u00e1i l\\u1ec5 Ph\\u1eadt<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>+ Ch\\u00f9a Ph\\u1eadt V\\u00e0ng Wat Traimit<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;\\u2013 M\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00f4i ch\\u00f9a linh thi\\u00eang nh\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc Th\\u00e1i Lan v\\u1edbi b\\u1ee9c t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Ph\\u1eadt V\\u00e0ng Golden Buhhdha n\\u1eb1m \\u1edf ch\\u00ednh \\u0111i\\u1ec7n - &nbsp;b\\u1ee9c t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Ph\\u1eadt V\\u00e0ng l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi: cao 3 m\\u00e9t v\\u00e0 n\\u1eb7ng h\\u01a1n 5,5 t\\u1ea5n. T\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00fac theo phong c\\u00e1ch Sukhothai t\\u0129nh l\\u1eb7ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u00ecnh c\\u1edd v\\u00e0o th\\u1eadp ni\\u00ean 1950 Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng cho r\\u1eb1ng b\\u1ee9c t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi n\\u00e0y bi\\u1ec3u th\\u1ecb cho s\\u1ef1 th\\u1ecbnh v\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 thu\\u1ea7n khi\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 s\\u1ee9c m\\u1ea1nh v\\u00e0 quy\\u1ec1n n\\u0103ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>+ Ch\\u00f9a N\\u00fai V\\u00e0ng (Wat Saket - Golden Mount ho\\u1eb7c \\u2018Phu Khao Thong\\u2019)<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ngon \\u0111\\u1ed3i th\\u1ea5p v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3o th\\u00e1p b\\u1eb1ng v\\u00e0ng l\\u1ea5p l\\u00e1nh. B\\u00ean trong, t\\u00f2a th\\u00e1p 58m c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a x\\u00e1 l\\u1ee3i Ph\\u1eadt v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00f3n ch\\u00e0o du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ebfn chi\\u00eam b\\u00e1i su\\u1ed1t n\\u0103m. Ng\\u00f4i ch\\u00f9a c\\u0169ng t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c l\\u1ec5 h\\u1eb1ng n\\u0103m v\\u00e0o th\\u00e1ng 10, di\\u1ec5n ra m\\u1ed9t tu\\u1ea7n trong su\\u1ed1t Loy Krathong (l\\u1ec5 h\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u00e8n hoa \\u0111\\u0103ng l\\u00ean tr\\u1eddi).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>Tr\\u01b0a:<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch \\u0103n Tr\\u01b0a t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh \\u0111i Pattaya, tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111i Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch tham quan Tr\\u1ea1i H\\u1ed5 Siracha Tiger Zoo xem c\\u00e1c ti\\u1ebft m\\u1ee5c bi\\u1ec3u di\\u1ec5n nh\\u01b0: xi\\u1ebfc h\\u1ed5, xi\\u1ebfc voi, xi\\u1ebfc l\\u1ee3n, xi\\u1ebfc c\\u00e1 s\\u1ea5u\\u2026<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>T\\u1ed1i:<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch \\u0103n T\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n MANTRA PURA RESORT&nbsp; ho\\u1eb7c t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 03: PATTAYA&nbsp; -&nbsp; CORAL ISLAND&nbsp; \\u2013&nbsp; WORLD GEM GALLERY \\u2013&nbsp; L\\u00c2U \\u0110A\\u0300I TY\\u0309 PHU\\u0301 \\u2013&nbsp; KHAO CHEECHAN \\u2013 COLOSSUEM SHOW&nbsp;&nbsp;(\\u0102N S\\u00c1NG \\/ TR\\u01afA\\/T\\u1ed0I)<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>S\\u00e1ng:<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch \\u0103n s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n. Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 xe \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111oa\\u0300n ra bi\\u1ec3n Pattaya, qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch l\\u00ean t\\u00e0u cao t\\u1ed1c \\u0110\\u1ea3o San H\\u00f4 (Coral Island). Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tham d\\u1ef1 c\\u00e1c tr\\u00f2 ch\\u01a1i nh\\u01b0: d\\u00f9 bay, c\\u00e2u c\\u00e1, l\\u01b0\\u1edbt v\\u00e1n, l\\u00e1i Scooter tr\\u00ean m\\u1eb7t bi\\u1ec3n, th\\u00e1m hi\\u1ec3m d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1y bi\\u1ec3n\\u2026(chi ph\\u00ed t\\u1ef1 t\\u00fac). Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 do t\\u1eafm bi\\u1ec3n Pattaya v\\u1edbi l\\u00e0n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong xanh, b\\u00e3i c\\u00e1t d\\u00e0i tr\\u1eafng m\\u1ecbn.Tr\\u01a1\\u0309 la\\u0323i \\u0111\\u00e2\\u0301t li\\u00ea\\u0300n, Quy\\u0301 kha\\u0301ch \\u0103n tr\\u01b0a t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>Chi\\u1ec1u:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span>Xe v\\u00e0 HDV \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111o\\u00e0n th\\u0103m quan:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>- Trung t\\u00e2m ch\\u1ebf t\\u00e1c V\\u00e0ng B\\u1ea1c \\u0110\\u00e1 Ho\\u00e0ng Gia Qu\\u00fd World Gems Gallery<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng v\\u00e0 l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a Th\\u00e1i Lan. N\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y c\\u00e1c t\\u00e1c ph\\u1ea9m ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00e1 qu\\u00fd c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c ngh\\u1ec7 nh\\u00e2n ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Th\\u00e1i: c\\u00e1c b\\u1ee9c t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00f4ng, h\\u1ed5, r\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n b\\u1eb1ng v\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e1 qu\\u00fd; c\\u00e1c b\\u1ee9c tranh kh\\u1ea3m \\u0111\\u00e1 qu\\u00fd: b\\u00e1t m\\u00e3, b\\u00e1t ti\\u00ean qu\\u00e1 h\\u1ea3i\\u2026. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, \\u0111\\u00e2y c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i di\\u00ea\\u0303n ca\\u0301c phi\\u00ean trao \\u0111\\u00f4\\u0309i mua ba\\u0301n \\u0111a\\u0301 quy\\u0301 \\u0111a\\u0323t ch\\u01b0\\u0301ng chi\\u0309 ISO 9002 v\\u00ea\\u0300 qua\\u0309n ly\\u0301 ch\\u00e2\\u0301t l\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0323ng, n\\u01a1i tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e1 qu\\u00fd \\u0111\\u1eb9p n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng, cung c\\u1ea5p nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng tin b\\u1ed5 \\u00edch v\\u1ec1 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh khai th\\u00e1c, ch\\u1ebf t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u00e1 qu\\u00fd t\\u1ea1i Th\\u00e1i Lan v\\u00e0 tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\">- L\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u00e0i t\\u1ef7 ph\\u00fa Baan Sukhawadee<\\/span>&nbsp;<\\/strong>- Co\\u0301 v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed ven bi\\u1ec3n, ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac ch\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea5y \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng ho\\u00e0ng cung, cung \\u0111i\\u1ec7n&nbsp;Versailles, mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1i nh\\u00ecn h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn v\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac, t\\u00f2a l\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u00e0i c\\u00f2n ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ef1ng nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd ngh\\u0129a \\u1ea9n v\\u1ec1 tri\\u1ebft l\\u00fd nh\\u00e2n sinh, t\\u00f4n gi\\u00e1o s\\u00e2u s\\u1eafc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>- Tr\\u00e2n Ba\\u0309o Ph\\u00e2\\u0323t S\\u01a1n Khao CheeChan<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;\\u2013 Ng\\u1ecdn n\\u00fai c\\u00f3 b\\u1ee9c t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0ng kh\\u1eafc b\\u1eb1ng Laze tr\\u00ean v\\u00e1ch n\\u00fai, d\\u00f9ng 999kg v\\u00e0ng, cao 130m. Xung quanh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c bao ph\\u1ee7 b\\u1edfi v\\u00f4 s\\u1ed1 lo\\u1ea1i hoa kh\\u00e1c nhau trong nh\\u1eefng khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9. Khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 b\\u1edfi H\\u1ea3i Qu\\u00e2n Ho\\u00e0ng Gia&nbsp;Th\\u00e1i Lan.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">- Xe \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111o\\u00e0n \\u0111i \\u0103n t\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111o\\u00e0n \\u0111i th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c&nbsp;<span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh Show Colloseum&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span>ch\\u1ec9 c\\u00f3 \\u1edf Th\\u00e1i Lan - Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, mang m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc c\\u1ee7a nhi\\u1ec1u qu\\u1ed1c gia do c\\u00e1c di\\u1ec5n vi\\u00ean chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i gi\\u1edbi t\\u00ednh bi\\u1ec3u di\\u1ec5n<em>.&nbsp;<\\/em>\\u0110o\\u00e0n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i t\\u1ef1 do kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u00eam.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n MANTRA PURA RESORT&nbsp; ho\\u1eb7c t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 04: PTY \\u2013 AQUARIUM PATTAYA \\u2013 V\\u01af\\u1edcN SAITHIP -&nbsp; TT NGHI\\u00caN C\\u1ee8U R\\u1eaeN \\u0110\\u1ed8C \\u2013 C\\u1eecA H\\u00c0NG \\u0110\\u1ed2 DA \\u2013 TRUNG T\\u00c2M TH\\u01af\\u01a0NG M\\u1ea0I&nbsp;&nbsp;(\\u0102N S\\u00c1NG\\/TR\\u01afA)<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>S\\u00e1ng:<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;Sau khi \\u0103n s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch tr\\u1ea3 ph\\u00f2ng. Xe \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111o\\u00e0n kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh v\\u1ec1 Bangkok. Tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111i gh\\u00e9 th\\u0103m:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>- C\\u00f4ng vi\\u00ean th\\u1ee7y cung Aquarium Pattaya<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;- N\\u1eb1m c\\u00e1ch trung t\\u00e2m th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 ch\\u1ec9 6km, Th\\u1ee7y cung Underwater World Pattaya l\\u00e0 \\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ea3o trong xanh t\\u1eadp trung v\\u00f4 s\\u1ed1 lo\\u00e0i sinh v\\u1eadt bi\\u1ec3n. \\u0110\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u00e2y, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i h\\u00f2a m\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0o th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng bao la v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn h\\u01a1i th\\u1edf bi\\u1ec3n c\\u1ea3 v\\u1edbi kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1edf 180\\u00b0 \\u0111\\u1ea7y ngo\\u1ea1n m\\u1ee5c.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>- V\\u01b0\\u1eddn Saithip (Saithip Garden)&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span>- L\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m 3 mi\\u00ea\\u0300n cu\\u0309a v\\u01b0\\u01a1ng qu\\u00f4\\u0301c Th\\u00e1i Lan. Qu\\u00fd kha\\u0301ch co\\u0301 th\\u00ea\\u0309 t\\u1ef1 do mua s\\u1eafm c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u0103\\u0323c sa\\u0309n nh\\u01b0: Huy\\u1ebft Y\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u00f3ng h\\u1ed9p, M\\u1eadt Ong thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean, cao h\\u1ed5 c\\u1ed1t,\\u2026).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>- Trung t\\u00e2m nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u R\\u1eafn \\u0111\\u1ed9c Ho\\u00e0ng Gia:<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c Show di\\u1ec5n b\\u1eaft r\\u1eafn b\\u1eb1ng tay kh\\u00f4ng, sau \\u0111o\\u0301 Quy\\u0301 kha\\u0301ch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0323c nghe ca\\u0301c d\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0323c sy\\u0303 gi\\u01a1\\u0301i thi\\u00ea\\u0323u v\\u00e0gi\\u1ea3i th\\u00edch v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng lo\\u00e0i r\\u1eafn q\\u00fay hi\\u1ebfm tr\\u00ean v\\u01b0\\u01a1ng qu\\u1ed1c Thailand v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i thu\\u1ed1c ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb r\\u1eafn m\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Th\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u00e3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u su\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n 100 n\\u0103m.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0, 128, 0)\\\"><strong>- C\\u1eeda h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ed3 Da(Leather Factory Outlets) n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng c\\u1ee7a Th\\u00e1i Lan<\\/strong><\\/span><em>.&nbsp;<\\/em>Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00e1ch ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e2n lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c s\\u