(517, 1, 'admin/tour-trong-nuoc/8', 'PUT', '127.0.0.1', '{\"code\":\"VIP10S17\",\"title\":\"Du l\\u1ecbch Th\\u00e1i Lan 5 ng\\u00e0y 4 \\u0111\\u00eam T\\u1eeb th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh tour \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1eafc\",\"slug_tour\":\"du-lich-thai-lan-5-ngay-4-dem-tu-thanh-pho-ho-chi-minh-tour-dac-sac\",\"amount\":\"10\",\"date_start\":\"H\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y\",\"start\":\"1\",\"country_id\":\"1\",\"description\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(178, 34, 34)\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 01: TP. H\\u1ed2 CH\\u00cd MINH - TH\\u00c1I LAN<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1eadp trung t\\u1ea1i: c\\u1ed5ng D2, c\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 12, l\\u1ea7u 02 \\u2013 Ga \\u0111i qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf&nbsp;<strong>T\\u00e2n S\\u01a1n Nh\\u1ea5t<\\/strong>. Tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111o\\u00e0n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam l\\u00e0m th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c.&nbsp;Chuy\\u1ebfn bay BL661\\u0111i Bangkok l\\u00fac 12:10. \\u0110\\u1ebfn&nbsp;<strong>s\\u00e2n bay qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf Suvarnabhumi<\\/strong>&nbsp;- s\\u00e2n bay l\\u1edbn v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i nh\\u1ea5t \\u0110\\u00f4ng Nam \\u00c1.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">HDV \\u0111\\u00f3n \\u0111o\\u00e0n, tham quan th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 Bangkok: D\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa t\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi m\\u00f3n l\\u1ea9u&nbsp;<strong>Suki Yaki<\\/strong>&nbsp;t\\u1ef1 ch\\u1ecdn. V\\u1ec1 kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, nh\\u1eadn ph\\u00f2ng, ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i Bangkok.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/du%20lich%20thai%20lan\\/baiyoke-sky-hotel-4-1.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:575px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:840px\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(178, 34, 34)\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 02: BANGKOK - TR\\u1ea0I H\\u1ed4 SRIRACHA PATTAYA<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">D\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, tr\\u1ea3 ph\\u00f2ng. Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 tham quan th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1<strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong>Bangkok: Ch\\u00f9a&nbsp;<strong>Wat saket&nbsp;<\\/strong>m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00f4i ch\\u00f9a n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng c\\u1ee7a<strong>&nbsp;Bangkok.&nbsp;<\\/strong>\\u0110\\u1ec3 l\\u00ean th\\u0103m ng\\u00f4i ch\\u00f9a, du kh\\u00e1ch ph\\u1ea3i leo 318 b\\u1eadc thang h\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea1ng xo\\u1eafn l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ec9nh n\\u00fai. Tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ec9nh n\\u00fai, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ng\\u1eafm to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea3nh Bangkok.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">D\\u00f9ng c\\u01a1m tr\\u01b0a, kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh v\\u1ec1 Pattaya. Tham quan tr\\u1ea1i h\\u1ed5&nbsp;<strong>Sriracha TigerZoo:<\\/strong>&nbsp;Xi\\u1ebfc c\\u00e1 s\\u1ea5u, Xi\\u1ebfc h\\u1ed5. Heo ch\\u1ea1y \\u0111ua, heo l\\u00e0m to\\u00e1n. Khu v\\u1ef1c nu\\u00f4i h\\u1ed5, c\\u00e1 s\\u1ea5u, h\\u1ed5 nu\\u00f4i heo, heo nu\\u00f4i h\\u1ed5. Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee5p h\\u00ecnh chung v\\u1edbi ch\\u00faa t\\u1ec3 s\\u01a1n l\\u00e2m to l\\u1edbn.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">\\u0110\\u1ebfn th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1&nbsp;<strong>Pattaya<\\/strong>, nh\\u1eadn ph\\u00f2ng, d\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa t\\u1ed1i.&nbsp;<strong>Tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m Massage c\\u1ed5 truy\\u1ec1n Thailan<\\/strong>&nbsp;gi\\u00fap l\\u01b0u th\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed huy\\u1ebft, h\\u1ed3i ph\\u1ee5c s\\u1ee9c kho\\u1ebb. Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 t\\u1ef1 do kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 bi\\u1ec3n v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u00eam, ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i&nbsp;<strong>Pattaya<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(10, 89, 212); text-decoration-line: none;\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/du%20lich%20thai%20lan\\/tour-du-lich-thailand-6n5d-massage-thai-co-truyen-tri-gia-500b-lau-suki-nhat-bbq-hai-san-2014122413442949.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:560px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:840px\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(178, 34, 34)\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 03: PATTAYA - NH\\u00c0 T\\u1ef6 PH\\u00da - ALCAZAR<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec3m t\\u00e2m t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, ra \\u0111\\u1ea3o san h\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng t\\u00e0u: \\u0110\\u1ea3o san h\\u00f4 n\\u1eb1m trong v\\u1ecbnh Thailan c\\u00f3 b\\u1edd c\\u00e1t tr\\u1eafng, l\\u00e0n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong xanh. Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 t\\u00fac t\\u1eafm bi\\u1ec3n ho\\u1eb7c tham gia c\\u00e1c tr\\u00f2 ch\\u01a1i ngo\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u1ea3o nh\\u01b0:&nbsp;<strong>L\\u1eb7n bi\\u1ec3n, M\\u00f4 t\\u00f4 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, d\\u00f9 k\\u00e9o, tr\\u00e1i chu\\u1ed1i, d\\u00f9 k\\u00e9o<\\/strong>\\u2026<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec1n, d\\u00f9ng c\\u01a1m tr\\u01b0a, ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn Trung t\\u00e2m World Gem n\\u01a1i tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i trang s\\u1ee9c b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u00e1 qu\\u00fd.&nbsp;<strong>Tr\\u00e2n B\\u1ea3o Ph\\u1eadt S\\u01a1n&nbsp;<\\/strong>t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Ph\\u1eadt kh\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ed3 b\\u1eb1ng v\\u00e0ng.&nbsp;<strong>V\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho<\\/strong>&nbsp;khung c\\u1ea3nh l\\u00e0ng qu\\u00ea Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c tham quan<strong>&nbsp;Baansukhawadee:&nbsp;<\\/strong>\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m\\u1ec7nh danh l\\u00e0 ng\\u00f4i nh\\u00e0 h\\u1ea1nh ph\\u00fac &nbsp;\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng tr\\u00e1ng l\\u1ec7, nguy nga b\\u00ean b\\u1edd bi\\u1ec3n, m\\u00f4 ph\\u1ecfng theo cung \\u0111i\\u1ec7n Versailles. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m tham quan m\\u1edbi v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn t\\u1ea1i Pattaya. L\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u00e0i l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t qu\\u1ea7n th\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a, \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng tri\\u1ebft l\\u00fd nh\\u00e2n sinh, t\\u00e2m linh s\\u00e2u s\\u1eafc.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">D\\u00f9ng c\\u01a1m t\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. Xem ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ea1i nh\\u1ea1c h\\u1ed9i n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng Thailan:&nbsp;<strong>Alcazar show<\\/strong>. Xe \\u0111\\u01b0a qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch v\\u1ec1 kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, t\\u1ef1 do kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u00eam, ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i Pattaya.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(10, 89, 212); text-decoration-line: none;\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/du%20lich%20thai%20lan\\/thai-lan6.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:473px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:840px\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(178, 34, 34)\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 04:&nbsp;PATTAYA - BANGKOK&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">D\\u00f9ng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m t\\u00e2m t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, tr\\u1ea3 ph\\u00f2ng, kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh v\\u1ec1 Bangkok, tham quan:&nbsp;<strong>V\\u01b0\\u1eddn b\\u01b0\\u1edbm \\u2013 Butterfly garden<\\/strong>: t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u00e0m ngh\\u1ec1 thu ho\\u1ea1ch t\\u1ed5 Y\\u1ebfn.&nbsp;<strong>Tr\\u1ea1i r\\u1eafn<\\/strong>: bi\\u1ec3u di\\u1ec5n v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c lo\\u00e0i r\\u1eafn, t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u v\\u1ec1 y h\\u1ecdc c\\u1ed5 truy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Th\\u00e1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><strong>Trung t\\u00e2m \\u0111\\u1ed3 da<\\/strong>&nbsp;n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng c\\u1ee7a Thailan. D\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa tr\\u01b0a t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng xoay&nbsp;<strong>buffet qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf Baiyoke sky&nbsp;<\\/strong>ng\\u1eafm to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea3nh th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 Bangkok t\\u1eeb tr\\u00ean cao. D\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa tr\\u01b0a &nbsp;v\\u1edbi h\\u01a1n 100 m\\u00f3n \\u0103n kh\\u1eafp th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0103n chay, ph\\u1ea7n \\u0103n chay \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb kh\\u00e1 chu \\u0111\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 tinh t\\u1ebf.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ec1u&nbsp;<strong>vi\\u1ebfng Ph\\u1eadt B\\u1ed1n M\\u1eb7t.<\\/strong>&nbsp;T\\u1ef1 do tham quan mua s\\u1eafm, d\\u00f9ng b\\u1eefa t\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c si\\u00eau th\\u1ecb nh\\u01b0&nbsp;<strong>BigC, Central World, Siam Paragon hay ch\\u1ee3 s\\u1ec9 Platinum, Pratunam\\u2026&nbsp;<\\/strong>\\u0110\\u1ebfn gi\\u1edd h\\u1eb9n xe v\\u00e0 HDv \\u0111\\u00f3n \\u0111o\\u00e0n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, ngh\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u00eam t\\u1ea1i Bangkok.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/du%20lich%20thai%20lan\\/bangkok-pattaya-tang-buffet-baiyoke-sky-86-tang-alcaza-show-tour-le-30-04-201532155922973.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:560px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:840px\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(178, 34, 34)\\\"><strong>NG\\u00c0Y 05: BABGKOK - CH\\u00d9A PH\\u1eacN V\\u00c0NG - TP. H\\u1ed2 CH\\u00cd MINH<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">D\\u00f9ng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m t\\u00e2m, tr\\u1ea3 ph\\u00f2ng, tham quan:&nbsp;<strong>Ch\\u00f9a Ph\\u1eadt V\\u00e0ng Wat Trimit<\\/strong>: ng\\u00f4i ch\\u00f9a linh thi\\u00eang n\\u1eb1m ngay trung t\\u00e2m Yaowarat. Chi\\u00eam ng\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng<strong>&nbsp;T\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Ph\\u1eadt V\\u00e0ng n\\u1eb7ng 5,500kg v\\u00e0ng<\\/strong>: b\\u1ee9c t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Ph\\u1eadt kh\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ed3 b\\u1eb1ng v\\u00e0ng nguy\\u00ean kh\\u1ed1i ch\\u1ee9a \\u0111\\u1ef1ng trong \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e2u chuy\\u1ec7n ri\\u00eang&nbsp; k\\u1ef3 th\\u00fa.&nbsp;<strong>D\\u1ea1o thuy\\u1ec1n tr\\u00ean s\\u00f4ng Chaophaya<\\/strong>&nbsp;huy\\u1ec1n tho\\u1ea1i, ng\\u1eafm m\\u1ed9t Bangkok kh\\u00e1c l\\u1ea1 t\\u1eeb d\\u01b0\\u1edbi s\\u00f4ng.&nbsp;<strong>Xem hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00e1 n\\u1ed5i tr\\u00ean s\\u00f4ng,<\\/strong>&nbsp;\\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 khu v\\u1ef1c g\\u1ea7n c\\u00e1c ng\\u00f4i ch\\u00f9a. Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 cho c\\u00e1 \\u0103n b\\u00e1nh m\\u00ec s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y hang tram ng\\u00e0n con c\\u00e1 n\\u1ed5i l\\u00ean chen k\\u00edn m\\u1eb7t song. \\u0110o\\u00e0n kh\\u1edfi h\\u00e0nh ra s\\u00e2n bay.D\\u00f9ng c\\u01a1m tr\\u01b0a Coupon t\\u1ea1i khu \\u1ea9m th\\u1ef1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">\\u0110\\u00e1p chuy\\u1ebfn bay&nbsp;<strong>BL662<\\/strong>&nbsp;l\\u00fac&nbsp;<strong>15h25&nbsp;<\\/strong>&nbsp;v\\u1ec1 Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u00e2n bay T\\u00e2n S\\u01a1n Nh\\u1ea5t: Nh\\u1eadp c\\u1ea3nh, nh\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh l\\u00fd, chia tay tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111o\\u00e0n, k\\u1ebft th\\u00fac chuy\\u1ebfn tham quan.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(35, 82, 124); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px;\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vietnamtravel.net.vn\\/media\\/images\\/du%20lich%20thai%20lan\\/wat-benjamaborphit-90427924.jpg\\\" style=\\\"border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:560px; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:840px\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"time\":\"5\",\"price\":\"6990000\",\"status\":\"1\",\"hot\":\"2\",\"_token\":\"GhFAK44lmkgkr94W8VdMrS3vP0RvdlspiZQLEC3J\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8000\\/admin\\/tour-trong-nuoc\"}', '2022-08-02 00:46:23', '2022-08-02 00:46:23'),
